# Docker
docker/data/

# --------------------------------------------------------------------------- #
# AI coding-tool local files — NEVER commit.                                  #
# These are per-developer tool memory/config, not project artifacts. Canonical #
# project documentation lives under /docs and /docs/ai-context (see README).   #
# A bare filename pattern matches at any depth.                               #
# --------------------------------------------------------------------------- #

# Claude Code / claude-mem (auto-generated memory & local config)
CLAUDE.md
.claude/
.claude-mem/

# Cursor
.cursor/
.cursor-rules/
.cursorrules
.cursorignore

# Aider
.aider*

# OpenAI Codex / GPT / generic LLM & AI tool files
.codex*
.gpt*
.llm*
.ai*

# Note: /docs and /docs/ai-context stay versioned — none of the patterns above
# match them (they have no leading dot, and the only CLAUDE.md inside them is a
# tool-generated stub that SHOULD be ignored). Project docs are *.md files there.
